creator: AllTaster
descriptionHtml:
Rewards are all that matter!
Have fun with a full Taster experience where every order counts!
Simply sign up to our loyalty program scan your order ticket's QR code and earn points! (1￡= 100 pts). Unlock points by completing challenges too! and become our favourite taster customer by ranking first and get featured on social media!
descriptionShort: Enjoy free rewards by unlocking points with every QR code you scan!
